# InnerCircles Tech Stack

This document outlines the technical stack used in the InnerCircles Android application.

## Core Technologies
- **Kotlin** (v2.0.0) - Primary programming language
- **Android Gradle Plugin** (v8.4.1) - Build system

## UI Framework
- **Jetpack Compose** (BOM v2024.06.00) - Modern UI toolkit
  - Material 3 (v1.2.1)
  - Compose Navigation (v2.5.3)
  - Compose Activity (v1.9.0)
  - Compose ViewModel (v2.6.1)

## Android Architecture Components
- **AndroidX Core KTX** (v1.10.1) - Kotlin extensions for Android core
- **AndroidX AppCompat** (v1.6.1) - Backward compatibility
- **Material Design** (v1.10.0) - UI components and theming
- **ConstraintLayout** (v2.1.4) - Flexible layout system
- **Fragment KTX** (v1.3.4) - Fragment management with Kotlin extensions
- **Activity KTX** (v1.2.3) - Activity management with Kotlin extensions

## Navigation
- **Navigation Component** (v2.6.0) - Navigation framework
  - Navigation Fragment KTX
  - Navigation UI KTX

## Lifecycle Components
- **Lifecycle ViewModel KTX** (v2.6.1) - ViewModel with Kotlin extensions
- **Lifecycle LiveData KTX** (v2.6.1) - LiveData with Kotlin extensions

## Networking
- **Retrofit** (v2.11.0) - HTTP client
- **Retrofit Gson Converter** (v2.9.0) - JSON serialization/deserialization
- **OkHttp Logging Interceptor** (v4.9.0) - Network logging

## Image Loading
- **Coil** (v2.1.0) - Image loading library
- **Coil Compose** (v2.7.0) - Compose integration for Coil

## Security
- **AndroidX Security Crypto** (v1.0.0) - Encryption utilities
- **Bouncy Castle** (v1.69) - Cryptography library

## Firebase
- **Firebase BOM** (v33.7.0) - Firebase dependency management
- **Firebase Messaging** (v24.1.0) - Push notifications

## Testing
- **JUnit** (v4.13.2) - Unit testing
- **AndroidX JUnit** (v1.1.5) - Android testing extensions
- **Espresso** (v3.5.1) - UI testing
- **Compose Testing** - UI testing for Compose

## Build Tools
- **KSP** (v1.9.0-1.0.11) - Kotlin Symbol Processing
- **Google Services Plugin** (v4.4.2) - Google services integration